<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٨٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١١٢٩٥ -<span class="c5"> عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ قَالَ:</span> وَقَالَ قَتَادَةُ: <span class="c2">«يُطَلِّقُهُنَّ جَمِيعًا»</span>. عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١١٢٩٦ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ، عَنْ جَابِرٍ، عَنِ الشَّعْبِيِّ مِثْلَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>